<tr><td>36</td><td>Ni iyihe feri ituma imodoka igenda buhoro kandi igahagarara ku buryo bwizewe bubangutse kandi nyabwo, uko imodoka yaba yikoreye kose yaba igeze ahacuramye cyangwa ahaterera:</td><td>Feri y’urugendo</td><td>Feri yo gutabara Feri yo guhagarara umwanya munini Nta gisubizo cy’ukuri kirimo</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
